Date: Wed, 17 Sep 2025 22:18:37 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:hostapd:Add MSCS in assoc and add cli
 support for MSCS

1. Advertise MSCS descriptor in assoc response
----------------------------------------------

* Add support to parse MSCS descriptor in assoc request sent by STA
* Add MSCS descriptor with status in the assoc response sent by AP

2. cli support
---------------

* Add cli support to send unsolicited MSCS response
* Add cli support to dump MSCS context for all associated STAs

Patch-dependency:
r94-01-UPSTREAM-hostapd-MSCS-Add-protocol-support-for-mscs.patch
Patch-work: NA
Tag: MSCS

Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
